I tried adding setHasShadow() to the winit library as @tomaskallup advised. It's working as expected.
```diff
--- winit-0.22.0.orig/src/platform_impl/macos/window.rs	2020-03-16 22:29:58.000000000 +0900
+++ winit-0.22.0/src/platform_impl/macos/window.rs	2020-03-17 01:09:11.000000000 +0900
@@ -223,6 +223,7 @@
                 }
             }

+            ns_window.setHasShadow_(NO);
             ns_window.center();
             ns_window
         });
```
